text: Hollywood Hillbillies is an American reality television series, based on CopperCab. It is about Claire Kittrell (better known as Claire Copper or his YouTube username CopperCab), his grandmother Delores "Mema" Hughes, his aunt Dee Dee Peters, and his uncle John Cox moving from their home in Grayson, Georgia to Hollywood, California. It aired on January 21, 2014. Category:American reality television series Category:Television spin-offs Category:2014 American television series debuts Category:2010s American television series
title: Hollywood Hillbillies
